Perhaps the most extraordinary design awaits customers in Längenfeld: Ötztal's water cathedral looks like a UFO that has just landed in the Alps.
From three open fountains steam rises in winter, while in the background the mountains of Ötztal rise in the sky.
Alhambra in the Black Forest
Meder, the pool collector, was not invaded by the smell of chlorine in all the pools.
